  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An old-school RPG adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone, or with up to four players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Either way, it tends to get out of hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find your way</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tears of Adria doesn’t care where you go, or why.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What it can’t stand is weaklings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden paths. Strange encounters. Rewards with no introduction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some things only exist if you notice them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/bc3c3b5b843c04c96611df281c221b2c.poster.avif?t=1774351958\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/bc3c3b5b843c04c96611df281c221b2c.webm?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/bc3c3b5b843c04c96611df281c221b2c.mp4?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Godly... or useless</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main character is locked in. Good luck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest are replaceable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/0570a35dd40b338f615331482e657579.poster.avif?t=1774351958\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/0570a35dd40b338f615331482e657579.webm?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/0570a35dd40b338f615331482e657579.mp4?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Autobattle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to understand. Difficult to get right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Positioning matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skills matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How they interact matters more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/20c647e526d23cfd27e0b624b8bda803.poster.avif?t=1774351958\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/20c647e526d23cfd27e0b624b8bda803.webm?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/20c647e526d23cfd27e0b624b8bda803.mp4?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ark Zahk — The Imp is not welcome in heaven.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An old-school RPG adventure</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play alone, or with up to four players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Either way, it tends to get out of hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find your way</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tears of Adria doesn’t care where you go, or why.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What it can’t stand is weaklings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden paths. Strange encounters. Rewards with no introduction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some things only exist if you notice them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/bc3c3b5b843c04c96611df281c221b2c.poster.avif?t=1774351958\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/bc3c3b5b843c04c96611df281c221b2c.webm?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/bc3c3b5b843c04c96611df281c221b2c.mp4?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Godly... or useless</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your main character is locked in. Good luck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The rest are replaceable.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/0570a35dd40b338f615331482e657579.poster.avif?t=1774351958\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/0570a35dd40b338f615331482e657579.webm?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/0570a35dd40b338f615331482e657579.mp4?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Autobattle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy to understand. Difficult to get right.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Positioning matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear matters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skills matter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How they interact matters more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/20c647e526d23cfd27e0b624b8bda803.poster.avif?t=1774351958\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/20c647e526d23cfd27e0b624b8bda803.webm?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2561500/extras/20c647e526d23cfd27e0b624b8bda803.mp4?t=1774351958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ark Zahk — The Imp is not welcome in heaven.</p>",
